        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Election Technology Integrity and Fraud Prevention Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a voting system used in a federal election from connecting to the internet. Further, it prohibits a voting system from directly tabulating a ballot that was transmitted online.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
